    "action": "tasks_refined",
    "detail": "Using Next.js 15 App Router with Server Components for admin dashboard (zero-client JS), cookie-based auth via middleware (no heavyweight auth lib), Resend for transactional emails with React Email templates, native fetch for Slack webhooks, GA4 via next/script (no react-ga4 wrapper for simplicity), static sitemap/robots.txt in public folder (no dynamic generation needed for 3-page site), Supabase Server Components pattern for data fetching.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-18 19:42:27"
  },
  {
    "id": 192,
    "company_id": "f18611ad-0434-47e9-bb7e-3e65ffea98e3",
    "agent_id": "cto",
    "task_id": "8e7f9f14-6711-4cb1-b120-802dbbb45319",
    "action": "tasks_refined",
    "detail": "Using Playwright over Puppeteer for better TypeScript support and cross-browser compatibility. Cheerio for HTML parsing due to jQuery-like API familiarity. OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo for translation (cheaper than GPT-4, sufficient quality for product names and addresses). Resend for email (simpler API than SendGrid, better deliverability than AWS SES for transactional). Vercel cron over external services (tightly integrated, no additional auth setup). Supabase Database Webhooks for event-driven architecture (eliminates polling, instant order relay). All secrets managed via environment variables with Vercel's encrypted storage.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-18 19:41:14"
  },
