    "detail": "Using Next.js 15+ App Router with Server Components for /success page (server-side Stripe/Supabase fetch), API Routes for /api/checkout and /api/webhooks/stripe. Supabase with RLS for data security (service role key only in server-side webhooks). Stripe Checkout (hosted) instead of embedded Payment Element for faster implementation. JSONB for shipping_address to support flexible international address formats. Zod for runtime validation. Tailwind v4 for styling. Test mode first, production keys added post-testing.",
